Reasoning: The paper discusses the application of neural networks in evolutionary algorithms for dynamic optimization problems. This falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the training of the neural network and the use of reliable samples, which relates to machine learning (cs.LG). The use of evolutionary algorithms for optimization falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY), and the application of these algorithms to robotics is also mentioned, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO).
